  "name": "Dawnbreaker Cohort",
  "titles": "Dawnbreaker Cohort",
  "lore": "Even within a Legion whose skills in the arts of orbital strike and shock assault are legendary, the Dawnbreaker cohorts stand apart. Chosen from amongst the most experienced and daring of the Legion’s assault squads, the Dawnbreakers are trained and equipped to act as the tip of the Blood Angels’ spear. Lacking the versatility of standard tactical or assault units, the Dawnbreakers have one purpose in battle: to sunder the enemy’s lines and tear the heart from its formation. Armed with lances and blades wreathed in keen-edged power fields, there are few warriors who can stand in the face of such an onslaught.",
